gg lego snow temple

This is a small sized symmetrical GG map. This is the second version in LEGO TEXTURES.  I left the layout the same but I've reworked the textures.
Buy Zones are included for Fight Yard style play too.

Please download, comment and enjoy!

- 64 Spawns
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Buy Zones
- Nav File
- Custom Lego Textures by boharox
- Pakrat
